{"word":"G1188 - δεξιός - dexiós - dex-ee-os' - Right","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δεξιός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dexiós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dex-ee-os'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Right</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வலது - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"the right"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1209 - δέχομαι - déchomai - dekh'-om-ahee/1209\">G1209</a>; the <i>right</i> side or (feminine) hand (as that which usually <i>takes</i>): - right (hand, side).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}